								<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
				<p>By submitting your email you agree Studio427 Audio will send you newsletters about the next product releases. Your address will not be shared, or used for any other purpose. Studio427 Audio guarantee the confidentiality of your information, and is not associated with any other third party. Respect is a key word at Studio427 Audio, and we intend to act as such. We use Mailchimp service for managing our newsletter and customers data. (<a href="https://mailchimp.com/legal/">more on the Mailchimp policy</a>) If you do not wish to receive newsletter from us anymore, you can unsubscribe from the mailing list at the bottom of any newsletter.</p>					</div>
